4
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:54,159
Zhang... Zhang Xiaobei.

5
00:00:54,399 --> 00:00:55,840
Show Mr. Zhu some respect.

6
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,320
Do you know what you're doing?

7
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,479
Stopping you from committing murder.

8
00:00:58,759 --> 00:00:59,320
You know him?

9
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,359
He's my boss.

10
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,840
You killed my sister!

11
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:17,000
Why didn't Sheng Yuanzhou say so then?

12
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,920
Why didn't he explain?

13
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:20,319
He actually admitted it.

14
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,560
That he caused my sister's death.

15
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:22,599
No, that's not right.

16
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:25,200
Sheng Shizhong gave the order.

17
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,840
But Sheng Shizhong...

18
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,760
Why pin it...

19
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,079
...on Sheng Yuanzhou?

20
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,120
Wait.

21
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:33,280
Don't tell me...

22
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,319
So that's it.

23
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:41,640
Sheng Shizhong used my sister's death...

24
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:43,200
...to pull strings behind the scenes.

25
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,760
First, he used the scandal...

26
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:46,040
...to drive the stock price down.

27
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,480
Then he bought in cheap.

28
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,840
Now he leaks the truth...

29
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,239
...and the price is bound to rebound.

30
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,680
In and out like that...

31
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,799
...he fleeced the small-time investors.

32
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,439
