33
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:03,920
No.

34
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,840
Those videos can't get out. Not ever.

35
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,599
I won't let my sister die...

36
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:10,800
...and still be used by them.

37
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:14,240
Zhu Zipeng, you won't get away with this!

38
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:17,719
Still not releasing the video?

39
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:24,560
Are you feeling pity for the dead again?

40
00:02:32,759 --> 00:02:33,520
I just...

41
