43
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:45,639
I want all of Sky Roc Entertainment.

44
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,280
Deep spring in the Bronze Terrace locks the two Qiaos.

45
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,719
In the past, Cao Cao had Bronze Terrace.

46
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,240
Today, the Zhu family has ours.

47
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,919
Take a look. What do you think?

48
00:03:04,759 --> 00:03:05,800
Babes.

49
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:06,960
Greet him.

50
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:10,039
Hello, Mr. Sheng.

51
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:12,319
Which one do you like?

52
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:13,800
Which one?

53
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:15,199
Pick anyone you want.

54
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,080
So?

55
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,240
At your annual party, I only...

56
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,479
...liked one of your secretaries.

57
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,759
Now I'm paying you back twentyfold.

58
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,000
That's fair enough, right?

59
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,840
I heard Mr. Zhu keeps...

60
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,560
...an expensive song and dance troupe.

61
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,000
Seeing them today...

62
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,680
...they really are something.

63
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:51,360
I handpicked every one of these girls.

64
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,199
Look at their figures.

65
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,560
Look at those faces.

66
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:56,039
None of them is over 25.

67
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,759
No wonder...

68
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:58,639
...you spend so much a year keeping them.

69
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:00,120
That's nothing.

70
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:02,080
Know how much money they make me?

71
