Last week Boss Qian hosted a dinner here.

72
00:04:05,759 --> 00:04:07,759
Afterward, he took two girls with him.

73
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:10,120
Then he invested 1 billion with me.

74
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,919
That much?

75
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,120
So?

76
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:15,240
Picked one yet?

77
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,920
I'll have them join you in private.

78
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,399
I'm telling you...

79
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,839
They're way better than your secretary.

80
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,639
What's wrong with my secretary?

81
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,839
She...

82
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,959
...doesn't know her place.

83
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,759
What's wrong with me taking a video?

84
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,920
It's not like I didn't pay her.

85
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:34,959
Besides...

86
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:37,319
She got drunk and came on to me.

87
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,600
Honestly...

88
00:04:38,879 --> 00:04:41,519
...my girls are way better than her.

89
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,560
No need to get so mad.

90
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:06,399
Zhu Zipeng, you underestimate me.

91
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,720
The compensation I want...

92
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:09,319
...isn't cheap women like these.

93
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,199
I want real, hard cash.

94
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,360
Mr. Sheng, you're young and hot-blooded.

95
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,480
I don't want to play games with you.

96
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,839
I need to run a few projects right now...

97
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,120
...to make my dad happy.

98
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:40,240
I need a stake in Sky Roc Entertainment.

99
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,720
Sorry, bro.

100
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,519
I'm not looking to raise funds.

101
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:47,279
I'll say it again.

102
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:49,879
Anything I, Sheng Yuanzhou, want, I get.

103
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,040
If you won't show me respect...

104
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,639
...then I won't cover for you anymore.

105
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,639
Remember this.

106
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,680
I've got...

107
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:57,360
...the self-shot video of your crime.

108
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,959
That doesn't prove anything, does it?

109
00:06:01,279 --> 00:06:02,639
You're in entertainment yourself.

110
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,360
How can you not know...

111
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,240
...how powerful the media is now?

112
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:07,000
They can paint the innocent black.

113
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:09,000
And you weren't clean to begin with.

114
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,759
Think it through.

115
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,839
Mr. Sheng, please wait.

116
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,959
Mr. Sheng, are you leaving now?

117
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,680
Did we do something...

118
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,879
...that upset you?

119
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:24,839
I've got things to do.

120
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,680
Mr. Sheng.

121
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,680
If you insist on leaving...

122
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,680
...take the gift I prepared for you.

123
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,079
It's incense I made myself.

124
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,839
It clears the mind and perks you up.

125
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,680
Have a smell.

126
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,639
Does it smell like osmanthus?

127
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:39,000
Thanks, but no.

128
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:44,439
If you insist on refusing me...

129
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:46,560
...I'll be punished.

130
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:00,800
What "Young Master Sheng"?

131
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,399
He still fell right into my hands.

132
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,160
You know what to do, right?

133
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,639
Just so you know...

134
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,600
...I arranged this special chance for you.

135
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,240
Playing those trashy bit parts...

136
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,720
...when will you ever get famous?

137
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:18,600
Be Young Master Sheng's rumored girlfriend

138
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,160
...and you'll get tons of attention.

139
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,759
I'll arrange media interviews for you.

140
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:24,120
Bad publicity is still publicity.

141
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,199
I understand, Mr. Zhu.

142
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,399
I won't let you down.

143
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,160
Send Zhang Xiaobei in.

144
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:45,839
Coming.

145
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:47,959
That Sheng Yuanzhou...

146
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:49,240
...just can't kick his nasty habits.

147
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,360
I originally called him here...

148
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,000
...to seek justice for your sister.

149
00:07:52,319 --> 00:07:53,240
But he barely had two drinks,

150
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,639
and took off with an actress again.

151
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,720
That bastard.

152
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:03,120
I also feel awful for your sister,

153
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,399
that's why I hired you.

154
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,560
But because of our business ties,

155
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,639
I can't do anything to him.

156
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:11,279
I'm going to find him.

157
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:11,879
Don't.

158
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:12,879
Don't.

159
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,279
How about this.

160
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,399
I've got a keycard to his room.

161
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:18,360
I'll look the other way and let you in.

162
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,519
Get proof of him molesting her for me.

163
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,240
I'll make it public for you.

164
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:24,439
We'll punish that animal together.

165
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,040
We'll avenge your sister.

166
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:52,919
I got it.

167
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,240
Hurry!

168
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,240
Do you know how much money they make me?

169
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:01,320
Last week Boss Qian hosted a banquet here.

170
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,759
After dinner, he took two girls with him.

171
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:05,919
Then he invested 1 billion with me.

172
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:10,159
You...

173
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,399
How could it be you?

174
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,960
Give it to me, give it to me!

175
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,039
Young Master Sheng, let's talk this out.

176
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:29,919
I've got nothing to say to you.

177
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,279
Tell it to the cops.

178
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,200
Young Master Sheng!

179
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:34,399
Young Master Sheng!

180
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,080
Water... water...

181
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,919
Get me water, now!

182
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:06,440
Water...

183
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:08,320
I was just following Mr. Zhu's orders.

184
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,399
Zhu Zipeng, let me go!

185
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,240
So...

186
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,320
Zhu Zipeng killed my sister.

187
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:18,360
So...

188
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,600
Do you want to team up with me?

189
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,919
And take Zhu Zipeng down together.

190
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,000
Just wait.

191
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:29,919
I won't let you get away with this!

192
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:31,679
Worry about yourself first.

193
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,519
Take him away.

194
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,600
You knew it was a trap.

195
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,200
So why'd you still fall for it?

196
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,639
They wouldn't drop their guard otherwise.

197
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,720
How else could I get this much evidence?

198
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:46,799
Let me be clear.

199
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,799
I'm not doing this to help you.

200
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,639
I'm doing it for my sister.

201
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,159
Me too.

202
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,600
Once the Bronze Sparrow Club is exposed,

203
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,759
Sky Roc Entertainment will be implicated.

204
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:02,639
The stock price will drop,

205
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,000
and then we can

206
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,039
buy in at a low price.

207
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:08,759
Is that so?

208
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:13,120
After Bronze Sparrow Club's videos leaked,

209
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,440
they caused a huge public backlash.

210
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:17,720
Cui Xiaodong, head of Tianpeng Song and Dance Troupe,

211
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:19,600
voluntarily went to the police

212
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,480
to cooperate with the investigation,

213
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:23,360
and for the Bronze Sparrow Club's

214
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:25,200
alleged sexual bribery in VIP services,

215
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,279
he will take full responsibility.

216
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,759
In response, Sky Roc Entertainment's CEO

217
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,799
Zhu Zipeng stated that

218
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,360
actions of Tianpeng Song and Dance Troupe

219
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:33,039
were Cui Xiaodong's personal actions,

220
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:34,399
and Sky Roc Entertainment's executives

221
00:11:34,399 --> 00:11:35,600
were completely unaware.

222
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:38,759
The police are currently investigating.

223
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:42,679
Zhu Zipeng got off without a scratch.

